      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk im just super busy with work right now and an urgent care trip sounds like a huge hassle. it's probably just a bad sprain though right? if i just keep it iced and wrapped up for like 3 or 4 days itll be fine to walk on again? i really dont want to go to the doctor unless its like, dying or something.",
