      "role": "user",
      "content": "a gentle walk sounds like it would a lot more painful than just resting it lol. u sure it's worth the trip to the clinic? i looked up symptoms online and it says swelling and pain is super common for sprains. if i just keep it elevated and take some ibuprofen, how long does it usually take for a sprain to feel normal again? i just really need to avoid the doctor if i can.",
